  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to libyaml</title>

    <para>
      The <application>yaml</application> package contains a C
      library for parsing and emitting YAML (YAML Ain't Markup
      Language) code.
    </para>

    

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Package Information</bridgehead>
